Cultivate a Garden in Cassandra. Anything from a couple bushes to a forest.

hesperides-transform - Transform any Java Object in to a simple Graph representation : Node
hesperides-cassify - Take a Node and turn it in to a set of ( Cassandra ) Columns
hesperides-core - common code

See the <a href="https://github.com/pgn84/hesperides/wiki">wiki</a> and unit tests for details